txt.en: Lend a hand in Skarháld by assisting Stráhek the Stout and by completing solo versions of the instances 'Thikil-gundu', 'Glimmerdeep', and 'Caverns of Thrumfall'. \n\n<rgb=#FF00FF>Every quest in these instances counts towards this goal.</rgb>

Lend a hand in Skarháld by assisting Stráhek the Stout and by completing Wanted Pebbles quests.\n\n<rgb=#FF00FF>Completing this quest will unlock Reclaiming the Grey II, and can be replayed weekly.</rgb>
There is much work to be done, if the Zhélruka hope to settle in the formidable Grey Mountains.
